data.description: Channel Front Living at Indian Lake!   Check out this very nice one-story home!  This home features 3 bedrooms, updated kitchen with granite counters, & new flooring.   Fun outdoor entertaining space under the covered porch facing the covered boat dock that includes a powered lift!   Other amenities include a detached 2 car garage, storage barn, carport, and small fenced yard.   Recent updates include a 22x16 addition that is currently used as the main bedroom with 2 walk-in closets, metal roof, and above ground pool.  In close proximity to Blackhawk, State Park, and walking/bike path or walk right over to the new Buckeye at the Lake for awesome food and spirits.  Call today for your private tour!!
